      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KARLI MULWEE (2) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 0.8 lengths at The Gardens in a handy 15.84 beating Hey Mac. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Will go close again if runs up to latest. JUST A JOY (1) jumped quickly from box seven to score (17.45) two back then drew the same last time but settled off pace and could manage only a 12 length 6th at this track (18.16). Got the money at her only try from this box. Can figure in the finish. MAJESTIC EMMY (7) was the early leader and copped a check in the run, boxing on well to finish a 4 length third (18.03) in a Grade 4 at this track. Key chance on best form. TRALEE AIMEE (8) solid chance again.",
